公司保安为了安抚司机发生的“轻微肢体接触和推搡动作”。至于随后该司进行报警处理，是为了“妥善处理纠纷”。 此前报道： 11月23日，一段“上海一货拉拉司机向保时捷工作人员维权”的视频，在社交平台引发关注。 货拉拉司机在视频中称，双方原本约定好600元的搬运费，但自己卸完货后，遭到保时捷工作人员赖账，并向平台投诉，导致自己被封号。 针对此事，记者采访了上海保时捷体验中心，工作人员回应，事件发生于21日，对该纠纷表示歉意，涉事人员是项目合作方的正式员工，双方已于当日达成和解，在日后的合作中，将提高对合作方人员的行为要求，加强在品牌活动现场的管理责任。保时捷不付货拉拉司机运费还打人，且投诉导致对方封号？保时捷回应"},"attached_info":"CkEIjbGq2s6SlP8BEAMaCTExMTk1MjQ0MSDa44O6BjAAOPAIQBNyCjQ4NzkwMjE5ODl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"4.9 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7e65c2040594ca151f3bb1ec5fbb48fe_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"20_1732436472.764193","card_id":"Q_4764399332","target":{"id":4764399332,"title":"如何看待《崩坏：星穹铁道》与加多宝的联名？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/4764399332","type":"question","created":1732189851,"answer_count":33,"follower_count":51,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[58688,781978],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAIjbGq2s6SlP8BEAMaCTExMTkyOTU0OCCbvfy5BjAAODNAFHIKNDc2NDM5OTMzMngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"4.6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-6c2004d93149f9b709e46c8d47504551_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"21_1732436472.764378","card_id":"Q_4849093353","target":{"id":4849093353,"title":"为什么南京民间习惯称“雨花区”，而不是官方正式名称“雨花台区” ？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/4849093353","type":"question","created":1732270060,"answer_count":71,"follower_count":145,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[285,1135,4421,7639,29876],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"为什么南京民间习惯称“雨花区”，而不是官方正式名称“雨花台区” ？"},"attached_info":"CkEIjbGq2s6SlP8BEAMaCT